source.name: Draft Additional Imagine Austin Indicators
source.description: The Imagine Austin comprehensive plan included numerous indicators that will be used to measure plan progress.  The indicators listed below are already closely tracked by other departments or agencies and are provided here to the public as a resource.  As new data and measurement techniques become available or as circumstances change, existing indicators may be revised, removed, and new ones added.
